This got a laugh from me, because I once tried to write a scip based on opossums, and after research came to the conclusion that if they weren't here in the real world already, they'd be an SCP item themselves. They can eat damn near anything organic in nature, they have a toxic scum on their fangs (to which they themselves are immune, naturally), and if they're attacked by anything they can't defeat, they can strike a pose in which they look, feel, and smell like they were killed a couple of weeks ago by some horrible disease.

And it gladdens my wizened old heart to see someone succeed where I failed.







